-- Czech Ex-President Klaus May Run for EU Parliament, Pravo Says
-- B y   P e t e r   L a c a
-- 2013-03-21T07:24:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-03-21/czech-ex-president-klaus-may-run-for-eu-parliament-pravo-says.html
Former Czech President Vaclav Klaus
is considering running in elections for the European Parliament
next year,  Pravo  said, citing an unidentified person.  Klaus may become the leader of conservative members of the
European assembly, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
